******Customizing Django's User Model*******

1. Extend User - Use-case:  For storing attribute related to authentication
In this same table is used for extra attributes
        User
         ^
         |
         |
       AppUser

2. Create Profile (Composition) - For storing non-auth related attributes like dob, address.
In this a new table is created and foreign keyed to User table

    Profile ---> User
